{
  "stem": "10862.3",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I would bring it home to this house where we stayed-- this bombed-out house-- and we would boil it in water and eat it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To today, I cannot stand a potato with peelings because it still reminds me of the potato peelings I ate, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we stayed there awhile in this city, Demblin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We wanted to wait and see if somebody would come, maybe somebody, somebody by a miracle would survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, nobody had.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed there till I think March, because I think we stayed a few months.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We waited there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was January.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We stayed until it got warmer, I think April or March.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had heard that the city of Lublin, which is not far from Demblin, which is about maybe 50 kilometer, it was sort of the gathering point of the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A lot of people were coming back to that, and they were organizing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They at that point already had an organization.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People were organizing, trying to put-- it was an army barracks and where they had army cots and that's where they organized all the people to come.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when you came there, you put-- they put names on a certain list of the survivors who survived.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So, in other words, whoever came back, they could see a name of people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, of course, you looked and you looked and you couldn't-- you couldn't find your own name.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
